4286:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           process the returned value with the helper macro
4287:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           @ref __LL_ADC_CHANNEL_TO_DECIMAL_NB().
