4408:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC data transfer mode
4409:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Conversion data can be either:
