6790:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be ADC disabled.
6791:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CR       DEEPPWD        LL_ADC_EnableDeepPowerDown
